        <p>Beachfront Oxnard sits on the Pacific from Hollywood Beach down through Silverstrand and Mandalay Bay to Channel Islands Harbor and Oxnard Shores — direct marine-air exposure, condo + beach-house housing, Sub-Zero / Wolf / Thermador kitchens common. Inland to the east, RiverPark Estates and the River Ridge / Windsor North area is newer-construction Ventura County luxury — RiverPark Marketplace shopping, golf-course communities, mainstream-luxury appliance brand mix. Downtown Oxnard around Heritage Square + Carnegie Art Museum + the Plaza Park has older homes and small commercial kitchens (restaurants, the Channel Islands Harbor marina businesses). South Oxnard around Rose Park is mid-market residential with mainstream appliance brands.</p>
